{"tid":448382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【鼻屎福利】殖民政府擬向綜援人士提供每月10元資助減輕廢物徵費負擔","createTime":"2017-10-26T07:11:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T07:22:58.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b05c087136b9d882e10e7e958d2e107a12ef513d","tid":448382,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:11:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1361415-20171026.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1361415-20171026.htm&d=4IF1C649KVaN%2BhE9NTL1iU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=6e37d1a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1361415-20171026.htm&h=100afd00\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1361415-20171026.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n環境局提出修訂固體廢物收費安排，建議擴大預繳式垃圾袋的適用範圍，私營廢物收集商、包括食環署的承辦商，只接收以指定垃圾袋包妥的廢物，原本的過渡安排「按桶」收費就會取消。<br />\n<br />\n環境局解釋，取消「按桶」收費，主要考慮到業界認為收費較高，可行性不高，為免令收費制度變得複雜，因此取消。<br />\n<br />\n另外，又提出向綜援人士提供每人每月10元資助，減輕廢物徵費帶來的負擔。以3人家庭為例，若每日用一個10公升指定垃圾袋，每月相關開支為33元，除開每人每月需付約10元相關費用。<br />\n<br />\n當局計劃年底向立法會提交修訂條例草案，最快2019年底實施有關安排。"},{"pid":"a8e85b023964323a6dd26644260a404fe09cde29","tid":448382,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:18:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊個天才局長諗？"},{"pid":"c38df6eb2fea9b8250fdd19d229bfdcc0822789c","tid":448382,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:20:01.000Z","msg":"班綜緩友真係多撚謝晒政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n33 蚊都唔全部資助，凈係出10蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d2645c910b176ba19c97ebfcd889d522b4ff78","tid":448382,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:20:24.000Z","msg":"加人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ba2f051316d5fd4df7a78385cd6dfe4f64ee2b","tid":448382,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:22:58.000Z","msg":"已包生養死葬<br />\n依+加送膠袋費"}]}